    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h3>Our main focus areas are as follows:</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Primary Health care for small domestic pets (mainly cats and dogs)</li>
              <li>Education with regard to pet care and nutrition</li>
              <li>In-patient care for the sick and wounded pets</li>
              <li>Sterilization as a means of controlling the burgeoning dog and cat populations</li>
              <li>Adoption kennels  for unwanted or stray animals</li>

            </ul>


